## Whonix is based on Debian testing.
deb http://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org testing main
#deb-src http://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org testing main

## Due to the botnet attack on Tor in September 2013, the rc of Tor 0.2.4
## works better than Tor 0.2.3 and there were no objections switching to
## Tor 0.2.4. We will use the tor-0.2.4.x-jessie repository, as long as
## Tor 0.2.4 isn't officially declared stable.
## See also, "[tor-talk] Should Whonix ship Tor 0.2.3 or 0.2.4?":
## https://lists.torproject.org/pipermail/tor-talk/2013-September/030012.html
deb http://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org tor-0.2.4.x-jessie main
#deb-src http://deb.torproject.org/torproject.org tor-0.2.4.x-jessie main
